
<h3 id="introduction">Blank Template</h3>
<p>Template for quickly building your web application in UIkit and PHP 7.<br/>This is an example of building an application using the MVC (Model-View-Controller) template when the layout, views (templates) and code are separated in a rather convenient way.</p>

